description:
HELLO future RACCOONZ owners
Thank you for choosing us. You know what you like and you seem to have very good taste ;)
We love you and swear eternal loyalty to you!

Each Raccoonz is a one-time generated NFT and cannot be imprinted a second time after it is generated.
The Raccoonz are generated in such a way that chance decides! There are different drawing styles.
This includes

Dress Styles:
-ARAB
-BODYBUILDER
-CAPTAIN
-GANGSTER
-PHARAOH
-RESEARCHER
-SAMURAI
-SOLDIER
-WILD WEST
-SECURITY
-SHIRT & JACKET
and secret others ;)

, facial expressions:
-SMILE
- SUPER SMILE
-STUPID LAUGH
-SERIOUS
-SAD
-BUBBLEGUM
and a few more :)

,
Accessories:
- PIERCING
-GLASSES
-CAPS
-HATS
-HAIR
-LOGOS
-TATTOOS
-UNICORN
and other very special ones ;oD

All RACCOONZ NFTs have been personally checked by me and are 100% unique


As a first-time buyer, you receive the status "CLUB MEMBER" and can move freely in RACCOONZ CITY.

We will start with this via discord and continue it on our upcoming website

In addition to active participation in the project, a club member is guaranteed various benefits and preferential purchases.
As an owner/first time buyer you will receive a membership in the #RCC Raccoonz City Club.

-Visit our Discord-
discord.gg/YpY2yjuGKm


You can have a say in the further course of the project like in a DAO, you will be rewarded for your loyalty, you will receive various discounts on future promotions and you will use your NFT to secure Raccoonz's total assets

WE LOVE U <3
name: IOTA RACCOONZ Season 1
